Insider Activity


Individual




Edmond J. English



Mr. Edmond J. English is Executive Chairman at Bob's Discount Furniture, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Burlington Stores, Inc., Rue La La, Boston Medical Center, Natixis Global Asset Management LP and Northeastern University. Mr. English was previously employed as Senior Vice President by The Marmaxx Group, Senior Vice President-Merchandising by T.J. Maxx, Inc., and President & Chief Executive Officer by The TJX Cos., Inc. He also served on the board at BJ's Wholesale Club, Inc. and Citizens Financial Group, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Northeastern University.



